data.description: Back on market! Welcome to the recently renovated 2616 Cloud Ct, Decatur, Ga where modern luxury meets comfortable living just 15 minutes from downtown Decatur. This residence showcases an array of carefully curated upgrades that transform each space into a stylish and functional haven. Once you enter, you are greeted by an inviting living room with plenty of natural light to fill the space, designed for both entertainment and relaxation. This living area features a stunning entertainment wall that accommodates your media needs, a cozy fireplace that radiates warmth, and tasteful shelving for displaying cherished memories. Next, you are welcomed by the new modern kitchen which features a pop of refreshing ocean blue that adds a vibrant touch to the space. This delightful color highlights the white cabinetry, providing a captivating contrast that's both stylish and charming. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, a tiled backsplash, the freestanding island, and new modern light fixtures. As you move up stairs, you are invited by the 4 bedrooms that each include their own closets and ample lighting to brighten the rooms. The master bedroom is a relaxing retreat featuring an ensuite bathroom with a soaking tub, a standalone shower, and dual vanity sinks. Beyond the interior, you'll find a well-maintained backyard and patio great for comfort and entertainment. The patio invites you with a comfortable open sitting area, a cozy fire pit to enjoy warmth and glow, as well as a char broil gas grill perfect for entertaining. This patio area isn't just great for entertaining but also gives you a place to unwind and enjoy the outside. Don't miss the opportunity to make this remarkable property your new home today. Contact Chelsea to schedule a showing!
